2026-01-30DFOFishing and Recreational Harbours ActRegulations Amending the Fishing and Recreational Harbours Regulations (Miscellaneous Program) Regulations Amending the Fishing and Recreational Harbours Regulations (Miscellaneous Program) in order to (1) update the list to remove 62 harbours from various provinces in Schedule I; (2) add three (3) harbours to various provinces in Schedule I; and (3) make the corrections to the name or location of five (5) harbours already in Schedule I.Registration: SOR/2026-0012 Publication Date: 2026-02-11
subject: Regulations Amending the Fishing and Recreational Harbours Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
precis: Regulations Amending the Fishing and Recreational Harbours Regulations (Miscellaneous Program) in order to (1) update the list to remove 62 harbours from various provinces in Schedule I; (2) add three (3) harbours to various provinces in Schedule I; and (3) make the corrections to the name or location of five (5) harbours already in Schedule I.
